OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening. Thickening cloud will bring a
OL,7,Ffew outbreaks of rain during the early
OL,8,Fhours, this turning persistent across
OL,9,FOrkney later. Freshening southeasterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRain spreading east during
OL,13,Fthe morning, clearing Orkney by late
OL,14,Fmorning and Shetland mid-afternoon.
OL,15,FBrighter weather following on behind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
