OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FEarly
OL,6,Fshowers on Friday otherwise dry and
OL,7,Fsunny. Windy with rain spreading
OL,8,Fnortheast on Saturday, Orkney drying
OL,9,Fup later. Breezy with a few showers on
OL,10,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
